name: Coleman Heating and Air Conditioning
overview: Coleman Heating and Air Conditioning was founded in 1998 by Jeff Coleman. Since inception it has grown into western Canada’s largest residential and commercial HVAC company. With an in-house metal fabrication warehouse, dozes of service trucks, 30+ employees, and a specialized duct cleaning truck. They work with local Vancouver based hosting providers to ensure optimal cooling in the data centers.
